org.eclipse.debug.core.commands

Interface ITerminateHandler

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IDebugCommandHandler

    public interface ITerminateHandler
extends IDebugCommandHandler
    A terminate handler typically terminates an executing thread or target.

    Clients may implement this interface. The debug platform provides a terminate action that delegates to this handler interface. As well, the debug platform provides an implementation of the terminate handler registered as an adapter on objects that implement ITerminate.

    Since:
    3.3
